Class KBRelation

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.KBID
      • adept.common.KBRelation

  • public class KBRelation
extends KBID
    The Class KBRelation represents a pointer to a Knowledge Base Entity uniquely identified by KB URI and source KB type. It derives from parent class KBID.
